From: Marcin FM <marcin@lgic.pl>
Subject: [PATCH] Discover ONNX Runtime in Fedora lib64

Search Fedora's architecture-specific ONNX Runtime installation path.

diff --git a/crates/kreuzberg/src/ort_discovery.rs b/crates/kreuzberg/src/ort_discovery.rs
--- a/crates/kreuzberg/src/ort_discovery.rs
+++ b/crates/kreuzberg/src/ort_discovery.rs
@@ -68,2 +68,3 @@ fn platform_candidates() -> &'static [&'static str] {
     &[
+        "/usr/lib64/libonnxruntime.so",
         "/usr/lib/libonnxruntime.so",
